      <title>反对党警告称，随着债务不断增加，泰国信用评级面临下调风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/thailand-risks-credit-rating-downgrade-as-debt-mounts-opposition-party-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国最大的反对派团体表示，如果泰国政府不控制巨额债务来支撑东南亚第二大经济体，该国信用评级将面临“非常令人担忧”的下调风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/thailand-risks-credit-rating-downgrade-as-debt-mounts-opposition-party-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:41:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行警告称，澳大利亚巨额养老金对稳定构成风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/rba-warns-that-australia-mega-pensions-pose-risks-to-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行警告称，该国 3.9 万亿澳元（2.7 万亿美元）养老金行业的迅猛增长给该国金融体系的稳定带来了新的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/rba-warns-that-australia-mega-pensions-pose-risks-to-stability</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:35:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本贸易局关注中国钢铁并提出反倾销提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/japan-trade-agency-eyes-chinese-steel-with-anti-dumping-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本经济产业省官员称，该省正寻求扩大反倾销税的范围，将中国钢铁等经第三国出口的产品纳入其中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/japan-trade-agency-eyes-chinese-steel-with-anti-dumping-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:17:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管美联储大幅降息，日元兑美元汇率仍跌至 145</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/yen-weakens-to-145-against-dollar-despite-jumbo-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商对日本和美国之间利差进一步缩小的速度仍不确定，日元兑美元跌至三周来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/yen-weakens-to-145-against-dollar-despite-jumbo-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑向顶级银行注资 1420 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-weights-142b-capital-injection-into-top-banks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，中国正考虑向其最大的国有银行注入 1 万亿元人民币或 1420 亿美元资本，以提高其放贷能力。彭博社中国通讯员 Minmin Low 与 Yvonne Man 和 David Ingles 在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中讨论了细节。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-weights-142b-capital-injection-into-top-banks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:46:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MBK 提高韩国锌业的收购报价，估值达 116 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/mbk-raises-korea-zinc-offer-price-to-attract-more-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MBK Partners 将其对韩国锌业公司控制权的主动出价提高了约 14%，推动该股创下历史新高，对这家全球最大锌冶炼厂的估值达到 15.5 万亿韩元（116 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/mbk-raises-korea-zinc-offer-price-to-attract-more-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:59:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
