    <item>
      <title>中国在长假前罕见发放补贴以提振市场人气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-announces-cash-handouts-for-the-poor-in-rare-use-of-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，将向困难居民提供一次性现金补助，并承诺为部分失业人员提供更多福利，以迅速推出一系列措施，旨在促进消费，缓解在重要国庆节前日益加剧的经济焦虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-announces-cash-handouts-for-the-poor-in-rare-use-of-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 10:37:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚央行认为林吉特将获得“持久支持”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-s-central-bank-sees-enduring-support-for-ringgit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚央行表示，鉴于马来西亚良好的经济前景和改革，林吉特的涨势可能持续下去。本周，林吉特攀升至三年来的最高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-s-central-bank-sees-enduring-support-for-ringgit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
